title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-30-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-30-2013 MON.............PODCAST




Monday, December 30, 2013


NY Times Benghazi Story

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest host, Ross Kaminsky.

 Discussion of blockbuster NY Times story claiming that Al Qaeda
       had nothing to do with the Benghazi attack on 9/11/12.
          It claims that the anti-Muslim video was the cause.

 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.

 - 11AM hour

What changes will legal pot make in Colorado culture, if any.
